Brief Summary of project:
A web application for the analysis and visualization of genomics data. The user could use it directly on web, which is convenient, and also uses it locally, which ensures privacy and security. 

The web application uses state-of-art statistical methods and provides visualization of the result. In addition, it guarantees the reproduction of the analysis by allowing user to download the work, and the user would be able to reproduce the work on any machine that installs R.
